These champions need Riot's help. Azir, Akali, Yorick, and Urgot are barely even viable and require a huge amount of mechanical knowledge just to do decent, not "survive" actually contributing to phases of the game.  

Gangplank is just all messed up right now. If you took the crit off the barrels and instead made them do 150%-170% of his bonus physical damage. They still nuke you but they aren't doing 600 damage a piece and wiping out an entire wave.
